title: Dolphins interested in Justin Herbert? Andy Dalton Landing Spots, Top 5 Free Agents Under 25 (Football 2/18)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to discuss the latest news and notes from the National Football League. The guys analyze if the Dolphins actually have interest in Justin Herbert and could potentially target the former Oregon QB over Tua Tagovailoa (7:45). The Pick Six Superfriends also discuss potential landing spots for Andy Dalton (16:20), Jameis Winston's future (28:00) and potential fixes for the Pro Bowl (42:00). Finally, Will, Ryan, John and Sean rank their Top 5 free agents under 25 in the NFL (48:00).

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
